1
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:08,080
Zhou Yi

2
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:12,320
Your room's pretty cluttered.

3
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:16,080
With my fragile heart,

4
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:17,640
who knows if I'll see tomorrow.

5
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:19,320
Gotta live it up while I can.

6
00:01:20,040 --> 00:01:21,680
Don't be so pessimistic.

7
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:24,080
You've still got Sister Bai and Lao Wang.

8
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:25,680
And besides,

9
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,520
you've got such a great home now.

10
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:33,200
I never even dreamed before

11
00:01:35,520 --> 00:01:37,560
that I'd have a room of my own.

12
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,680
This is your home from now on.

13
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:45,720
From now on,

14
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:48,000
there'll be your toothpaste on the mirror,

15
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,440
food saved for you in the pot,

16
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:52,720
and your socks on the couch.

17
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,440
Of course,

18
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:57,800
you can wash my socks for me too.

19
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,000
How about it?

20
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,360
About the socks thing,

21
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:07,320
you'd better handle that yourself.

22
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,680
But I can teach you a few tricks.

23
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,160
Next time you go out scaring people,

24
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,360
you might find them useful.

25
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:15,360
No, no, no.

26
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,320
Keep them for yourself.

27
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:17,120
I'm not learning that.

28
00:02:18,160 --> 00:02:19,320
You two little brats!

29
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,160
Dinner's ready!

30
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,000
Coming!

31
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,680
Welcome, Lin You! Cheers!

32
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,280
That hits the spot!

33
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,120
What are you doing, Lao Wang?

34
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:36,760
Fill it up again, fill it up!

35
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:37,800
Okay, okay, okay.

36
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:38,360
Lin You,

37
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,600
don't you dare nurse your drink.

38
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:40,440
Sister's got her eye on you.

39
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,520
Nurse my drink?

40
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:42,640
Let me tell you, Sister,

41
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:44,320
the four of you combined

42
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:45,440
might not even outdrink me.

43
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:48,000
He's challenging me!

44
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,200
Lin You,

45
00:02:49,200 --> 00:02:51,600
how can you say that in front of Sister Bai?

46
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:53,960
She's the Ghost's Bane of our street.

47
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,080
Super tough!

48
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:55,680
That's right.

49
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,520
Ghost's Bane, huh?

50
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,840
She really is the Ghost's Bane.

51
00:02:58,280 --> 00:03:00,280
Half the bottle ended up on the floor.

52
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,240
What a loss for the ghosts!

53
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,200
That's the Ghost's Bane for you.

54
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,920
Why are you taking their side?

55
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,640
What's going on here?

56
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:05,400
Come on, come on.

57
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:07,520
Come on, have a drink!

58
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:09,280
Everyone, eat well, drink well!

59
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,520
Don't worry about saving me money!

60
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:12,480
Cheers! Welcome, Lin You! Come on!

61
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:13,680
Welcome, Lin You!

62
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,120
Liu Liu.

63
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,959
You really can't hold your liquor.

64
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:18,959
You need practice.

65
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,640
Don't make her drink anymore.

66
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:22,920
She's just a young girl.

67
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:23,960
No more drinking.

68
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:24,800
She's already passed out.

69
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,000
A young girl like her,

70
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,600
can't even outdrink an old man like me.

71
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,720
She just needs practice.

72
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,400
Who needs practice?

73
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,640
You wanna challenge me?

74
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,480
Damn right!

75
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:41,120
I'll drink you under the table right now.

76
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,000
You wanna drink with me?

77
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,160
You wanna challenge me, Lao Wang?

78
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,240
Yaoyao, I'll drink with you.

79
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,480
If you can hold it, drink more.

80
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,600
Drink him under the table! Picking on Liu Liu, huh?

81
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:50,840
My apprentice's got skills!

82
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:51,480
Come on, come on.

83
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,800
Master will drink with you. And you know what,

84
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,600
you're next after this.

85
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:55,960
Come on.

86
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,120
Fifteen, twenty, fifteen!

87
00:04:58,200 --> 00:04:59,760
Fifteen, twenty, fifteen! Fifteen, twenty, twenty!

88
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:00,680
Drink!

89
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,680
Who lost?

90
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,360
Come on, kid.

91
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,200
You can't handle it.

92
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:03,960
Take a picture of us.

93
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,880
Let's take a picture together.

94
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:08,800
Come on.

95
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:10,480
Three, two, one.

96
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,040
Quick, quick!

97
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:13,040
Cheese!

98
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:16,600
Here, here.

99
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,520
Come on, let's keep going.

100
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:18,240
I want a redo!

101
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,640
I really want a redo this time. Wait a sec.

102
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:20,480
Come on, wait a sec.

103
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:22,000
I've got a new game now.

104
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:22,440
Listen up.

105
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:23,560
It's called "Catch the Butterfly."

106
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,040
Do you know it?

107
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,880
Let's play, let's play.

108
00:05:24,880 --> 00:05:25,360
All right, watch.

109
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,040
Catch the butterfly, catch the butterfly!

110
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:27,840
How many did I catch?

111
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:28,360
Eight!

112
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,240
Wrong!

113
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,560
Why? Five then!

114
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:31,960
Master.

115
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:32,960
Master got it right.

116
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:33,560
You drink.

117
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,800
One more round, one more round.

118
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,560
How did you even catch them?

119
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,440
I didn't get it at all.

120
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,480
Are you crazy? Why didn't you dodge?

121
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:09,000
That was way too dangerous just now.

122
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:10,440
I just stepped out to buy some booze,

123
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,760
and you almost got hit by a car.

124
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:12,720
That was so dangerous!

125
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:14,120
You tired of living?

126
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:26,000
The one who should be sitting here with you

127
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,120
shouldn't be me.

128
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:32,800
Out with it.

129
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,800
It's so late.

130
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:34,840
Why'd you call me out here?

131
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,880
I just want to know,

132
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,040
what really happened between you two?

133
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:46,040
Why did things end up like this?

134
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:01,120
We've known each other since we were little.

135
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:13,200
This was her birthday gift to me.

136
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:17,080
She knew I loved listening to music.

137
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:26,640
Ever since she was little, Liu Liu

138
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:29,160
was always the kind of kid grown-ups called

139
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,640
"the perfect child."

140
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,800
But only I knew

141
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:37,480
that she actually needed protecting.

142
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,240
So,

143
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:43,320
I always protected her.

144
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,480
Until...

145
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,320
Until that car accident.

146
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,600
But if it weren't for that accident,

147
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:04,720
Liu Liu might never have met all of you.

148
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,400
The accident?

149
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:13,360
To put it simply,

150
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:13,880
Whoosh!

151
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:14,360
Bam!

152
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,000
Ah!

153
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:16,360
And then I died.

154
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,680
After that,

155
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:28,680
Liu Liu became a completely different person.

156
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,600
Can you understand?

157
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:40,559
A girl who was already so fragile

158
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:45,040
watched her best friend

159
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,720
die right in front of her.

160
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:51,640
So...

161
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,840
After that, you just...

162
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,080
Yeah.

163
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,680
So I stayed.

164
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,520
You know,

165
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:10,640
Liu Liu is always so gentle,

166
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,960
so understanding,

167
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:15,080
always thinking of others.

168
00:09:19,560 --> 00:09:20,760
I couldn't bear

169
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:23,280
to let her face this world alone.

170
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:26,840
If I weren't there,

171
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:30,000
how much suffering would she endure?

172
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:33,960
So,

173
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,720
I should stay and protect her.

174
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:46,760
Then...

175
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:49,320
does Yaoyao know how you feel?

176
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:58,360
I mean Liu Liu.

177
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:05,160
But it can't go on like this forever.

178
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:09,040
Didn't Lao Wang say

179
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:11,800
that dwelling on this

180
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,720
is hurting you?

181
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,600
It's not good for either of you.

182
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:20,320
Yeah.

183
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,080
I was worried about that too.

184
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,120
But then,

185
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,680
I met you, didn't I?

186
00:10:32,800 --> 00:10:33,920
After you showed up,

187
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:35,800
I realized

188
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:37,400
that Liu Liu now has

189
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:39,200
one more person to look after her.

190
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,360
And I've decided,

191
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:46,600
once Liu Liu lets go of the past,

192
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,440
I can finally

193
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,480
entrust her to you with peace of mind.

194
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,280
And then,

195
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,360
leave.

196
00:10:59,080 --> 00:10:59,800
Wait.

197
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:00,480
You...

198
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:03,240
You didn't call me out to a place like this

199
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:05,200
just to hear my story, did you?

200
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,240
Whatever it is, just say it.

201
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:09,880
No.

202
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:12,960
This place is very important to me.

203
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,160
Since I was little,

204
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:20,360
I had no parents.

205
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,920
I wandered the streets

206
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:24,640
with my big brother from the orphanage.

207
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:29,400
This was my first home.

208
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,680
Today everyone said

209
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,440
they consider me family.

210
00:11:38,640 --> 00:11:39,680
So I thought,

211
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:41,520
I'd bring you here

212
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,360
to show you what means the most to me.

213
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:54,200
Didn't a book say

214
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,040
letting someone you care about

215
00:11:56,280 --> 00:11:57,520
know your past

216
00:11:58,520 --> 00:11:59,480
makes it easier for her

217
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,560
to come into your life?

218
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,720
Even though

219
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:08,160
my past isn't anything to be proud of,

220
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:09,960
but,

221
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:11,600
I just feel...

222
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:12,320
Thank you.

223
00:12:16,880 --> 00:12:20,640
Thank you for letting me into your life.

224
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:23,480
You big oaf.

225
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:27,160
No matter what happened in your past,

226
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:28,840
I'll always believe in you.

227
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,040
Come here.

228
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:43,440
Let me play you my music.

229
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:50,640
My music,

230
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:53,040
I don't share it with just anyone.

231
00:13:35,680 --> 00:13:36,480
Lin You

232
00:13:38,280 --> 00:13:39,280
I'm so grateful

233
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:41,160
that in such a complicated world,

234
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:43,000
I got to meet someone as pure as you.

235
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:44,360
Don't ever change.

236
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:47,080
Stay true to yourself.

237
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:15,760
Hello?

238
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:16,840
Where are you?

239
00:14:18,640 --> 00:14:19,280
I'm...

240
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:21,320
on my way to take Liu Liu home.

241
00:14:22,800 --> 00:14:23,480
Liu Liu?

242
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:25,440
All right.

243
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:26,400
Sister Bai's worried about you.

244
00:14:26,400 --> 00:14:27,520
She wants you back soon.

245
00:14:28,280 --> 00:14:29,120
I got it.

246
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,520
I'll head back in a bit.

247
00:14:31,040 --> 00:14:31,840
Don't worry.

248
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:32,600
Okay.

249
00:14:32,640 --> 00:14:33,280
I'm hanging up.

250
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:42,600
If you dare tell anyone about today,

251
00:14:43,560 --> 00:14:44,760
you're dead.

252
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:49,760
Well, I told you my stuff too.

253
00:14:51,520 --> 00:14:52,160
So...

254
00:14:54,880 --> 00:14:55,680
we're even.

255
00:14:59,640 --> 00:15:00,520
Hurry up and go.

256
00:15:00,800 --> 00:15:02,120
Sister Bai and the others will get anxious.

257
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:03,680
Take your booze with you!

258
00:15:17,680 --> 00:15:18,680
Take it easy.

259
00:15:18,680 --> 00:15:20,040
I'm fine.

260
00:15:21,040 --> 00:15:22,600
Slow down, you don't need to hold me.

261
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,400
Were you crying just now?

262
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:25,640
You're kidding.

263
00:15:25,880 --> 00:15:26,560
I wasn't!

264
00:15:26,640 --> 00:15:27,200
No way.

265
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,880
Yeah, keep denying it.

266
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:33,000
Look at me.

267
00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:49,440
Don't worry.

268
00:16:49,880 --> 00:16:50,760
I promise you.

269
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:52,560
I'll keep Liu Liu safe.

270
00:16:53,560 --> 00:16:54,360
I think

271
00:16:54,880 --> 00:16:56,360
Liu Liu's lucky to have a friend

272
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:58,240
like you.

273
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:25,680
What are you looking at?

274
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:51,200
Yaoyao, don't worry.

275
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:54,360
I'll make him pay for this.
